All Implemented Interfaces:
ca.uhn.fhir.rest.server.IResourceProvider
public class StructureMapListProvider extends StructureMapResourceProvider
The provider of the StructureMap/$list operation.

This operation allows listing all StructureMaps and retrieving a minimal subset of fields. The summary mode includes almost all fields of StructureMap, leading to huge responses. This operation is useful for clients that need to display a list of StructureMaps (e.g. name or url), but do not need all the details of each StructureMap.

Author:
Quentin Ligier
